{"tid":2171800,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【限聚令延長】消息：限聚令及晚市禁堂食等防疫抗疫措施再延長","createTime":"2020-08-24T08:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T08:10:35.000Z","uid":51665,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d672ed0ad3cc09a689dc03c2f2a0a54c1496d238","tid":2171800,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2730000/2733192/royn20200810027_1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2730000%2F2733192%2Froyn20200810027_1024_1024.jpg&h=a23bf06b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然政府已實施兩人限聚令及晚市禁堂食措施逾一個多月，但本港新冠肺炎疫情仍持續。消息稱，今日增9宗確診個案，為7月5日以來首次回落至單位數字。不過，消息指，原訂明天（25日）屆滿的兩人限聚令及晚市禁堂食等防疫抗疫措施，擬再延長一周。政府擬在完成為期兩周的全民檢測後，才考慮放寬限聚令。<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測將於9月1日起開始，初步預計為期7天，再按進度延期不多於7天。<br />\n<br />\n下次係9月8號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edab710d91c4d626d8b60d6de892d0f0c5a7b91","tid":2171800,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"又係hket，上次佢話開得晚市"},{"pid":"999ccaabe0ef9809645b6379f4c89798b09668b8","tid":2171800,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a20e1e3c1f09c58bb72e62ed86a026f835d99bb","tid":2171800,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"永續囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6850566e431b47c12c2f793bffde5010dfc9536","tid":2171800,"uid":119591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3edab710d91c4d626d8b60d6de892d0f0c5a7b91","tid":2171800,"uid":25357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:04:15.000Z","msg":"又係hket，上次佢話開得晚市"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"